race.comment: ALL WHISKEY (1) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only a long neck (25.47) behind Paw Gaeton at Warrnambool. Must come into calculations. IDYLLIC JAMES (6) was a last start winner (22.30) at Warragul who is building a strong winning record. Solid record here including five wins. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. OVERLAND BOY (4) has a strong record this trip with four wins and four placings from 11 starts. Was out of placings last time (30.98) at The Meadows in a Grade 5 H, finishing eighth and beaten 15 lengths. Can feature in the finish. PAW UELLA (2) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.
